snippet.title: Disgaea 1 Complete - A True Remasterpiece (Nintendo Switch, PS4)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ disgaea.us/d1c
Pre-order today! http://bit.ly/D1Complete

"Haaah-hahahaha!"

The OVERLORD of strategy RPGs returns! Join Laharl, Etna, and Flonne in their crazy adventure through the Netherworld to crown a new Overlord. Remastered for a new generation, with brand new visuals!
